{"tid":2152577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共拘捕　參考新疆發展：頭面人物→唔出名但一直活躍嘅人→平民","createTime":"2020-08-12T05:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T05:27:31.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a38311d1fd62a56a55e7d6587b7e08dda7d3ad6","tid":2152577,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EeymBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EeymBY.png&h=f4bcc4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n被警方以「港版國安法」通緝的本土民主前線前召集人黃台仰認為，香港問題為中美矛盾的一部份，「當中共認為美方採取行動打擊中共時，中共亦以拘捕佢哋認為嘅『美方棋子』作為反擊」。<br />\n<br />\n黃認為，中共必然會繼續用「港版國安法」拘捕香港人，「參考新疆嘅發展，中共會先將佢哋認為有影響力以及『就手』嘅人拘捕，然後依據佢嘅計算，順住影響力排名拘捕」，相信下一步很大機會會是打國際線的社運人士，以及勝出初選的激進派，「當呢啲頭面人物要拉嘅拉晒，要走嘅走晒之後，就會開始針對唔出名但一直活躍嘅人，最後就會好似新疆咁針對平民」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/U66Y32AWUP6TBTTH6YVIEVBQGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FU66Y32AWUP6TBTTH6YVIEVBQGU%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfxX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=b24420b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FU66Y32AWUP6TBTTH6YVIEVBQGU%2F&h=b27d07f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/U66Y32AWUP6TBTTH6YVIEVBQGU/</a>"},{"pid":"4d788a0cef883bc093fc0b40c078690db2cc7415","tid":2152577,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"好彩仲有BNO逃生門"},{"pid":"8c25b8841cd6349de048e1f9dfa3cae12bf55157","tid":2152577,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"無佢地就無蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2152353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2152353</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}